Package com.csci4448.project.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Checkout
    This class creates getters and setters for card and id and has a helper function to associate each card with an id.
    Customer
    This class creates getters and setters for all the variable used in different classes.
    Flight
    This class creates getter and setter for the variables in Flight and has a helper function Flight that holds information for a flight that is used in the FlightController class.
    Location
    This class creates getters and setters for variables used in the PathFinder class and has a helper function to associate a city with an id.
    Memento
    This class has the state of the object that is going to be restored.
    MementoState
    MementoState uses Memento by creating and storing the states in Memento objects.
